Subdue.help: Subdue deals moderate Psionic damage and may leave the targeted foe Immobilized for a brief time. Immobilized foes cannot move but can still attack. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate
Subdue.targetHelp: You have been Subdued and are being held immobile.

Repel.help: Repel creates a zone of kinetic energy that violently repels nearby foes. Each villain that is repelled costs additional Endurance. Recharge: Slow
Repel.attackerHit: You protect yourself with your {PowerName}, and will knock down any villain that approaches you.

Siphon_Power.help: The Hero has Siphoned your power and reduced your damage potential to strengthen his own.

Siphon_Speed.help: The Hero has Siphoned your speed and reduced your damage potential to increase its own.
Siphon_Speed.targetHelp: The Hero has Siphoned your speed and reduced your damage potential to increase its own.

Fulcrum_Shift.help: Fulcrum Shift drains the power of a targeted foe and all foes nearby, transferring it to all adjacent allies, the caster, and those near the caster. Affected foes will deal less damage, while your affected allies will deal more. The more foes that are affected, the more power your allies receive. Fulcrum Shift can dramatically turn the tide of a melee battle. Recharge: Long
Fulcrum_Shift.targetHelp: Your damage potential has been reduced.

Psychic_Shockwave.help: Psychic Shockwave is a devastating Psionic attack that wracks the minds of all nearby foes. Affected foes may have a reduced attack rate and may be left Disoriented. Damage: High Recharge: Slow
Psychic_Shockwave.targetHelp: The Psychic Wail has reduced your attack rate.
